{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, at one point, my father was teaching in a public school, in a religion, because in the public school, everybody had to learn religion.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish children had the class with a Jewish teacher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he would teach us baruhk and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the children didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- when he asked, how do you say-- what [YIDDISH] do you say for such and such, I'd raise my hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he would say, not you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got so insulted, [LAUGHS] because he know I knew it, and he wanted to teach the others.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that, I you used to hold against him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I couldn't talk in class, because I was able to show off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he just simply wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at one point, he taught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you that he did all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose, in retrospect-- I guess I still have resentment towards him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in retrospect, I really shouldn't have as much of resentment as I always did, because for one thing, it was in the 1930s, which was a worldwide recession.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Morris told many times how-- Who's Morris?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My former husband.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you many times how he used to go right here in Chicago with patched pants and-- and stockings, and how he used to ask for a nickel from his mother.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, no, we can't do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, for ice cream or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So things were difficult all over the world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, at the time, I didn't realize it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But actually, it was difficult everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
